---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Sponsor an Animal
description: Put a face and name on your support. Sponsor a permanent resident at SARA Sanctuary and help cover food, vet care, and shelter for the animals who live here for life.
permalink: /sponsor/
---

<header class="page-head photo-head" style="background-image: url('/images/sanctuary-july-2025.webp');">
  <div class="container">
    <span class="eyebrow">Sponsor</span>
    <h1>Put a face and name on your support.</h1>
    <p>Many of our animals will live at SARA for the rest of their lives. Sponsorship is the direct way to cover their food, medical care, and shelter, and to stay connected to the animal you help.</p>
  </div>
</header>

<section>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="prose">
      <span class="eyebrow">How It Works</span>
      <h2>Pick an animal. Cover their care. Get the updates.</h2>
      <p class="lede">Sponsorship is a monthly or one-time gift earmarked to a specific resident. You'll receive photos, stories, and updates from the sanctuary about the animal you sponsor.</p>

      <div class="info-grid">
        <div class="info-box">
          <div class="k">Monthly Sponsorship</div>
          <div class="v">Starting at $25/mo</div>
        </div>
        <div class="info-box">
          <div class="k">One-Time Sponsorship</div>
          <div class="v">Any amount</div>
        </div>
        <div class="info-box">
          <div class="k">Full-Year Sponsorship</div>
          <div class="v">$1,500 (dogs/cats)</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p>Dogs and cats cost roughly $1,500 a year to care for. Larger residents like horses, donkeys, and alpacas run into the thousands. Whatever amount you can give keeps an animal fed, protected, and treated.</p>

      <div style="display: flex; gap: 0.75rem; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 1rem;">
        <a href="/give/" class="btn btn-primary">Start a Sponsorship &rarr;</a>
        <a href="mailto:{{ site.emails.tracy }}" class="btn btn-ghost">Email Tracy</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section style="background: var(--cream-2);">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="center" style="max-width: 640px; margin: 0 auto 2rem;">
      <span class="eyebrow">Permanent Residents</span>
      <h2>Meet a few of the animals waiting for a sponsor</h2>
      <p class="muted">Every resident has a story. Here are a few of the animals who call SARA home for life.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-grid">
      <article class="card" style="padding: 0; overflow: hidden;">
        <div style="aspect-ratio: 4/3; background: url('/images/ducks.webp') center/cover;"></div>
        <div style="padding: 1.5rem;">
          <span class="pill sage">Rooster</span>
          <h3 style="margin: 0.5rem 0;">Barnyard Residents</h3>
          <p class="muted">Our barnyard fowl, pigs, and goats are often surrendered by families who can no longer care for them. They need steady monthly support.</p>
          <a href="/give/" class="btn btn-ghost btn-sm">Sponsor &rarr;</a>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="card" style="padding: 0; overflow: hidden;">
        <div style="aspect-ratio: 4/3; background: url('/images/horses.webp') center/cover;"></div>
        <div style="padding: 1.5rem;">
          <span class="pill sage">Large Animals</span>
          <h3 style="margin: 0.5rem 0;">Horses, Donkeys &amp; Mules</h3>
          <p class="muted">Large animal care is expensive. Our equines need hay, farrier visits, and routine vet care every month of the year.</p>
          <a href="/give/" class="btn btn-ghost btn-sm">Sponsor &rarr;</a>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="card" style="padding: 0; overflow: hidden;">
        <div style="aspect-ratio: 4/3; background: url('/images/adoptable.webp') center/cover;"></div>
        <div style="padding: 1.5rem;">
          <span class="pill">Dogs &amp; Cats</span>
          <h3 style="margin: 0.5rem 0;">Seniors &amp; Special Needs</h3>
          <p class="muted">Some of our dogs and cats will never be adopted due to age, medical issues, or temperament. They deserve sponsors who will see them through.</p>
          <a href="/give/" class="btn btn-ghost btn-sm">Sponsor &rarr;</a>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>

    <p class="center" style="margin-top: 2rem;">
      <a href="mailto:{{ site.emails.tracy }}" class="btn btn-primary">Ask About a Specific Resident</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="prose">
      <span class="eyebrow">What Sponsors Get</span>
      <h2>Direct connection to the animal you support.</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Photos and updates from the sanctuary</li>
        <li>Recognition on our website and sponsor wall (optional)</li>
        <li>A sponsor certificate with your animal's story</li>
        <li>Tax-deductible receipt (we're a 501(c)(3), DLN {{ site.ein }})</li>
        <li>Standing invitation to visit your sponsored animal at SARA</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="cta-strip">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="cta-strip-grid">
      <div>
        <h2>Ready to sponsor an animal?</h2>
        <p>Start a monthly commitment or make a one-time gift. Tracy will help you pick the right match.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="btns">
        <a href="/give/" class="btn btn-primary">Sponsor Now</a>
        <a href="mailto:{{ site.emails.tracy }}" class="btn btn-ghost">Email Tracy</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
